{"tid":1462884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完今日兩個記者會之後 覺得林鄭同白衫狗有樣嘢好值得大家學習","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:15:07.000Z","uid":26405,"like":119,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1b860594095abe6ec1be667e06635cbb7fc48114","tid":1462884,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論啲狗做咗幾多仆街嘢<br />\n<br />\n就算柒到俾人影低埋斷正<br />\n<br />\n都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔夠完美 可以改善</span></strong>咋<br />\n<br />\n簡直將<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不分化 不割蓆</strong></span>呢句表現得淋漓盡致<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地成日話兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n一遇到少少唔合自己意見嘅嘢就喺度互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地行到今日呢一步 就係靠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和而不同 團結合作</span></strong>呀<br />\n<br />\n有咩意見咪提出來傾個共識出來囉<br />\n<br />\n畀你地屌埋呢個post<br />\n<br />\n跟住好出返去傾下一步點做喇下！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"443d9a1bb87ba24472b34b88a8bd9b0cf847de78","tid":1462884,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"56efe3a54f790f4ce377a5cfa25139dcffc8f11e","tid":1462884,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"aef2d9b6b815ad4475f9bf8d12b771abf357715f","tid":1462884,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"acd39e4454a65b0f3d9c2f680bf94bb81c393bf4","tid":1462884,"uid":26405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"e6b65068c4d55801d389c7cf0e3b920f138c4fe0","tid":14628